Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.http.api.service.mapping.annotations.parameters.form

Annotation Type FormParam

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(PARAMETER)
public @interface FormParam
    Defines a form parameter. This annotation is applied to a Parameter that represents a parameter of a query of http request/parameter of x-www-form-urlencoded request body.
    See Also:
    QueryParameter, URLEncodedParameter

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      boolean allowReserved  
      boolean explode  
      FormStyles style  

    • Element Detail

      • explode

        boolean explode
        Returns:
        to explode parameter value or not. Default value is true. This has an effect when parameter value has type Map or type of some POJO.
        Default:
        true

      • allowReserved

        boolean allowReserved
        Returns:
        to percent-encode reserved characters or not. These characters are kept as they are when it is true
        Default:
        false

      • style

        FormStyles style
        Returns:
        style of a form parameter. Default is FormStyles.FORM
        Default:
        ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.http.api.service.mapping.annotations.parameters.form.FormStyles.FORM
